                                <decoNote>
                                    Handritið er í blágrárri pappírskápu (<dimensions
                                        type="binding" unit="mm" scope="all">
                                        <height>372</height>
                                        <width>245</width>
                                    </dimensions>) og safnmark fremst á kápu. Það er varðveitt í öskju (<dimensions unit="mm"><height>384</height><width>303</width><depth>67</depth></dimensions>) ásamt <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-I">KBAdd 35 I 4to</ref>, <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-II">KBAdd 35 II 4to</ref>, <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-III">KBAdd 35 III 4to</ref>, <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-IV">KBAdd 35 IV 4to</ref>, <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-V">KBAdd 35 V 4to</ref>, <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-VI">KBAdd 35 VI 4to</ref> <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-VII">KBAdd 35 VII 4to</ref> og <ref type="ms" target="#KBAdd04-0035-VIII">KBAdd 35 VIII 4to</ref>.
                                    <p>Stimpill frá <name type="org" key="KB">Konungsbókhlöðunni í
                                        Kaupmannahöfn</name> er á bl. <locus from="1r" facs="#KBAdd04-0035-IX-0001r" to="1r">1r</locus> og <locus from="3r" facs="#KBAdd04-0035-IX-0003r" to="3r">3r</locus>.</p>
                                        </decoNote>
                            </binding>
                        </bindingDesc>
                        <accMat>
